{"title":"Blacksmith Cycle and Bradley Harms Special Projects by Givelo","link":"https://theradavist.com/blacksmith-cycle-and-bradley-harms-special-projects-by-givelo/","date":1714573872000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2104\" height=\"1403\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?fit=1200,1403&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?w=2104&amp;quality=75 2104w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-holding-colour-paintings.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blacksmithcycle.com/en-us/collections/blacksmith-cycle-ss24\" target=\"_blank\">Blacksmith Cycle</a> out of Toronto pinged artist <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bradleyharms/\" target=\"_blank\">Bradley Harms Special Projects</a> on a run of cycling apparel inspired by the artist’s “Flow State” series and produced by <a href=\"https://givelo.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Givelo</a> in Medellín, Colombia. Let’s take a closer look.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3233\" height=\"2156\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?fit=1200,2156&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?w=3233&amp;quality=75 3233w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-BHSP-x-GIVELO-2024x-COVER.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The project takes on Bradley Harms’ approach to line and color and translates it to various cycling apparel pieces with earth tone hits. The collection consists of both tech tees and traditional jerseys, bibs, socks, and other riding staples, as well at lifestyle pieces. It’s open for pre-order today with arrival in May 2024.</p>\n<p>See the full drop at <a href=\"https://blacksmithcycle.com/en-us/collections/blacksmith-cycle-ss24\" target=\"_blank\">Blacksmith Cycle</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/blacksmith-cycle-and-bradley-harms-special-projects-by-givelo/\">Blacksmith Cycle and Bradley Harms Special Projects by Givelo</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4775500f6c3d7c8bd6593b01389843c7e41239691612e819433965be3aecf775","category":"Cycling"}